'''''Mandabi''''' (Igifaransa: '''''Le Mandat''''', "The Money Order") ni filime yo mu 1968 yanditswe kandi iyobowe n'umukinnyi wa filime wo muri Senegali Ousmane Sembène . Iyi filime ishingiye ku gitabo cya Sembène cyitwa ''The Money-Order'' kandi ni filime ya mbere y’umuyobozi mu rurimi rwe kavukire rwa Wolof . Kubera ko benshi mu baturage ba Senegal batumva igifaransa, Sembène yashakaga guhanga sinema kubavuga Wolof. Iyi niyo filime ya mbere yuzuye  ururimi nyafurika kuva muri Afrika y'uburengerazuba. 

== Umugambi ==
Umuyisilamu wo muri Senegal udafite akazi, Ibrahima Dieng, abana n'abagore be babiri n'abana barindwi i Dakar . Mwishywa we, Abdou, yohereje we kugira amafaranga kuva Paris agaciro 25.000 y'amanyarwanda, akaba yarakijjwe no gukubura mu muhanda. Ibrahima akabika amafaranga ye wenyine, akazigamira mwishywa we, agaha mushiki we umugabane.

== Kwandika ==
Nyuma yuko iyi filime itari imaze imyaka igera ku bantu bareba sinema, yasubiwemo mu mwanzuro wa 4K maze itangwa mu iserukiramuco rya Lumière rya 2019 ryabereye i Lyon mu Bufaransa.  Muri Kamena 2021, iyi verisiyo yasubiwemo yerekanwe muri sinema mu [[Ubwongereza|Bwongereza]] .
